{"title":"The New Lithic by Wolf Tooth Carbon Mountain Fork May Be the Most Versatile Rigid Fork","link":"https://bikerumor.com/lithic-by-wolf-tooth-carbon-mountain-fork-most-versatile-rigid-fork/","date":1692301092000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_1-Large.jpeg\" alt=\"Lithic Carbon Mountain bike fork front\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_1-Large.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_1-Large-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_1-Large-800x534.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_1-Large-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_1-Large-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_1-Large-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>Back in 2016, when Otso Bicycles grew from Wolf Tooth Components, we were introduced to a new component brand, Lithic. At the time, Lithic was mostly an OEM house brand for Otso to spec their bikes with various components, Lithic has slowly grown into a brand of its own. Now, Wolf Tooth is calling it ‘Lithic by Wolf Tooth’, likely for the brand recognition, but the goal remains the same – to create high-quality components that often include details not found elsewhere. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_5-Large.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_5-Large-800x534.jpeg\" alt=\"Lithic Carbon Mountain bike fork brakes\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_5-Large-800x534.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_5-Large-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_5-Large-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_5-Large-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_5-Large-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_5-Large.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_2-Large.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_2-Large-800x534.jpeg\" alt=\"Lithic Carbon Mountain bike fork crown\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_2-Large-800x534.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_2-Large-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_2-Large-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_2-Large-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_2-Large-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_2-Large.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_4-Large.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_4-Large-800x534.jpeg\" alt=\"Lithic Carbon Mountain bike fork side brake shot\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_4-Large-800x534.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_4-Large-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_4-Large-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_4-Large-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_4-Large-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_4-Large.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Take their new Mountain Fork for example. On the surface, it’s a rigid carbon MTB fork, but as soon as you start digging into the details you realize that this fork may be the most versatile on the market.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Post-Mount_F-Large.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Post-Mount_F-Large-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"Lithic Carbon Mountain bike fork\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Post-Mount_F-Large-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Post-Mount_F-Large-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Post-Mount_F-Large-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Post-Mount_F-Large-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Post-Mount_F-Large.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Flat-Mount_G-Large.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Flat-Mount_G-Large-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"Lithic Carbon Mountain bike fork\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Flat-Mount_G-Large-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Flat-Mount_G-Large-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Flat-Mount_G-Large-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Flat-Mount_G-Large-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Flat-Mount_G-Large.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Thanks to four different droput options, the fork will fit 15 x 110mm Boost hubs <em>or</em> 15 x 100mm non-Boost hubs, both with post mount or flat mount brake options. From there, the dropout flip chip can be used to adjust the offset/rake from 44mm to 51.5mm. Better still, flilpping the dropout chip still preserves your brake adjustment. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_10-Large.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_10-Large.jpeg\" alt=\"Lithic Carbon Mountain bike fork\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_10-Large.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_10-Large-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_10-Large-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_10-Large-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_10-Large-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Lithic-Carbon-Mountain-Fork_10-Large-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a><figcaption>Interesting looking cages. </figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Suspension corrected for 120mm travel forks, the Mountain Fork has a 495mm axle-to-crown with the 44mm offset, or 498mm A2C with the 51.5mm offset. Offereing tire clearance up to 29 x 3.0″, the fork is only offered with a 1 1/8- 1 1/2″ tapered steerer. External brake routing makes it a cinch to swap between your rigid fork and a suspension fork when needed, and the three-pack mounts on each fork leg make it perfect for bikepacking duties.  </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Flat-Mount_E-Large.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Flat-Mount_E-Large-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"Lithic Carbon Mountain bike fork\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Flat-Mount_E-Large-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Flat-Mount_E-Large-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Flat-Mount_E-Large-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Flat-Mount_E-Large-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Flat-Mount_E-Large.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Post-Mount_B-Large.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Post-Mount_B-Large-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"Lithic Carbon Mountain bike fork\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Post-Mount_B-Large-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Post-Mount_B-Large-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Post-Mount_B-Large-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Post-Mount_B-Large-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Post-Mount_B-Large.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Post-Mount_D-Large.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Post-Mount_D-Large-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"Lithic Carbon Mountain bike fork\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Post-Mount_D-Large-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Post-Mount_D-Large-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Post-Mount_D-Large-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Post-Mount_D-Large-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Post-Mount_D-Large.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Post-Mount_C-Large.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Post-Mount_C-Large-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"Lithic Carbon Mountain bike fork\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Post-Mount_C-Large-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Post-Mount_C-Large-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Post-Mount_C-Large-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Post-Mount_C-Large-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Mountain-Fork_Post-Mount_C-Large.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Lithic Carbon Mountain Fork specs:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Weights with dropouts and axle:\n<ul>\n<li>Flat mount 110mm Boost – 754g</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Flat mount 100m non-Boost – 776g</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Post mount 110mm Boost – 761g</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Post mount 100mm non-Boost – 781g</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Tapered steerer tube: 1 1⁄8” – 1 1⁄2”, 275mm uncut length</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Brake mount is swappable – post mount is 160mm, flat mount is 160/180mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li>15mm thru axle</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Offset/rake is adjustable – 44 or 51.5mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li>495mm axle-to-crown with 44mm offset, 498mm with 51.5mm offset</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Tire clearance 29” x 3.0”</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Suspension-corrected for 120mm suspension fork</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Fork includes 15mm thru axle, expander plug, and brake cable guide</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Price: $629.95 USD</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Lithic Carbon Gravel Fork &amp; Fat Fork</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Unlike the Mountain Fork, the Lithic Carbon Gravel Fork and Fat Fork (below) have been avaialble for some time as original equipment on Otso bikes. Both have fixed offset numbers, brake standards, and hub widths, but still offer a rigid carbon option for those that need it. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Carbon-Gravel-Fork_White-On-Bike_1-Large.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Carbon-Gravel-Fork_White-On-Bike_1-Large-800x534.jpeg\" alt=\"Lithic Carbon gravel bike fork on bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Carbon-Gravel-Fork_White-On-Bike_1-Large-800x534.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Carbon-Gravel-Fork_White-On-Bike_1-Large-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Carbon-Gravel-Fork_White-On-Bike_1-Large-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Carbon-Gravel-Fork_White-On-Bike_1-Large-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Carbon-Gravel-Fork_White-On-Bike_1-Large-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Carbon-Gravel-Fork_White-On-Bike_1-Large.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Carbon-Gravel-Fork_White_PDP_E-Large.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Carbon-Gravel-Fork_White_PDP_E-Large-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"Lithic Carbon gravel bike fork\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Carbon-Gravel-Fork_White_PDP_E-Large-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Carbon-Gravel-Fork_White_PDP_E-Large-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Carbon-Gravel-Fork_White_PDP_E-Large-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Carbon-Gravel-Fork_White_PDP_E-Large-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Carbon-Gravel-Fork_White_PDP_E-Large.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Carbon-Gravel-Fork_White_PDP_B-Large.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/LITHIC23_Carbon-Gravel-Fork_White_PDP_B-Large-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"Lithic Carbon gravel bike fork\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/